This is highly rated and I am most grateful for chance to sample it. Maybe others should step outside Marvel ous universe from time to time ;)

Yeah, there are A LOT of great comics outside of DC/Marvel to experience. I just hope someone scans issues #7 and #8 at some point. If you liked this, download The Killer (links in description) very highly acclaimed
